  Locus:
    Page: 137
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Evil
---
Even in evil, that dark cloud that hangs over creation, we discern rays of
light and hope, and gradually come to see, in suffering and temptations,
proofs and instruments of the sublimest purposes of wisdom and love.
